WEBVTT

00:00.566 --> 00:02.334
Previously on Underground...

00:05.070 --> 00:06.371
The longer we stand out here fightin',

00:06.405 --> 00:08.006
the less chance we got
of gettin' Rosalee back.

00:08.041 --> 00:09.208
Who knows what they doin' to her?

00:09.242 --> 00:11.196
Ain't nobody care about that house girl.

00:13.381 --> 00:15.884
We have to disrupt
their happy little lives.

00:18.853 --> 00:21.390
Anyone tries to follow me,
your massa gets it.

00:23.958 --> 00:25.661
He's not the massa.

00:25.695 --> 00:27.698
I am.

